'''IC-40X1-CRE''' was the [[Imperial Trade and Commerce Authority|Imperial Commerce]] permit needed to take [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorian]] [[shamarok flitter]]s past customs at [[Lianna/Legends|Lianna]]. Only [[Starship/Legends|ships]] with a livestock transport rated main cargo hold could qualify for this permit.

